{"tid":945251,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【中台票房報捷】《水行俠》台灣開畫四天破億 威過《神奇女俠》","createTime":"2018-12-17T17:15:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T04:56:19.000Z","uid":52215,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"87f619d18117a63354384911cb1731135b0b47f1","tid":945251,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T17:15:27.000Z","msg":"DC超級英雄大作《水行俠》（Aquaman）安排聖誕檔在香港上映，男、女主角積遜莫瑪（Jason Momoa）、安芭赫德（Amber Heard）及導演温子仁（James Wan）早前到北京宣傳，還破例在中國率先上映，截至今日短短11天已累積13億人民幣票房。<br />\n<br />\n台灣方面，《水行俠》上星期喺當地開畫，四天票房已衝破1億台幣（約2,535萬港元）大關，比五天破億台幣嘅《神奇女俠》（Wonder Woman）成績更加驕人！"},{"pid":"30d046f4617759c1599ae1ea63a77dfae3df8974","tid":945251,"uid":212399,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T17:18:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/iLA5wpfH1itK8/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FiLA5wpfH1itK8%2Fgiphy.gif&h=4609f1bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0148f6e25e297c4e252747ee73ccb3872e528604","tid":945251,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"30d046f4617759c1599ae1ea63a77dfae3df8974","tid":945251,"uid":212399,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T17:18:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/iLA5wpfH1itK8/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FiLA5wpfH1itK8%2Fgiphy.gif&h=4609f1bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T23:18:46.000Z","msg":"咪撚戇鳩啦"},{"pid":"ec459c568276822206c00afd955a071f4f457106","tid":945251,"uid":35746,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T23:22:33.000Z","msg":"marvel 是但一套都屌打架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11a208217a1a7a1460b858f521dc2e8a782b4e0","tid":945251,"uid":159183,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"ec459c568276822206c00afd955a071f4f457106","tid":945251,"uid":35746,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score"